name: Something About Us
wikiSummary: "Something About Us" is a song by the French electronic music duo Daft Punk. It was released as the final single from the 2001 album Discovery as a promotion for their 2003 animated feature film Interstella 5555: The 5tory of the 5ecret 5tar 5ystem. The song reached #93 on the SNEP chart ranking.
wikiText:
"Something About Us" is a song by the French electronic music duo Daft Punk. It was released as the final single from the 2001 album Discovery as a promotion for their 2003 animated feature film Interstella 5555: The 5tory of the 5ecret 5tar 5ystem. The song reached #93 on the SNEP chart ranking.
